{"tid":546703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三串炸小食賣近50元，台網民:呢種會有回頭客，港網民：好抵食","createTime":"2018-01-31T18:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T08:15:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"20efee0a59b491e3d7a9badf2740cc3948c4c48f","tid":546703,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:38:03.000Z","msg":"　<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/01/023710_d76f68894127b8ea0c66eda6d7f8a171.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F01%2F023710_d76f68894127b8ea0c66eda6d7f8a171.png&h=987cf948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n01月30日(二) 06:00   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180130/photo/bkntw-20180130060053988-0130_04011_001_01p.jpg?20180130060356\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180130%2Fphoto%2Fbkntw-20180130060053988-0130_04011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180130060356&h=60fee0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有網民發文指，日前到西門町一間連鎖式小食店買了鹽酥雞、豆腐及一款長條狀炸物，不僅份量少，就連價格也讓人吃驚。（網上圖片）</span><br />\n繼墾丁和台北夜市先後傳出食物定價不合理，近日再爆料西門町一個鹽酥雞檔懷疑「劏客」，3串份量極少的炸物竟要價180新台幣（約48港元）。有網民看後嘲諷「在鬼島沒標清價格的，這樣算你撿到喔！」 <br />\n<br />\n爆料者在Facebook專頁「爆料公社」指出，朋友日前到西門町一間連鎖式小食店買了鹽酥雞、豆腐及一款長條狀炸物，不僅份量少，就連價格也讓人吃驚。爆料者將食物拍照上網求網民評理，「大家說看看你覺得這樣的價錢合理嗎？還是因為反應店租成本人事成本，這樣是合理的呢？」爆料者又質疑「又在坑殺觀光客？」<br />\n<br />\n發文引發網民熱議，有人認為價格不合理︰「台南180也吃到吐」、「高雄180可以吃爽爽」、「這種價錢不會有回頭客」；有網民卻不以為意︰「嫌貴&hellip;別吃就好，應該不難」、「西門町還有很多便宜的東西吃吧，問清楚價錢在吃啊」；另外有人認為昂貴的租金才是物價貴的主因︰「房東的房租貴，怪誰」、「西門町的話這樣價格合理。有一半的淨利潤是房東賺去了」"},{"pid":"44d1f31a1a8ce431f6f1a90119fea196e72da6a0","tid":546703,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:40:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180130/mobile/bkntw-20180130060053988-0130_04011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Ftw%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180130%2Fmobile%2Fbkntw-20180130060053988-0130_04011_001.html&d=zEBK3YvARoZsHEwA%2BxTlJTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=524f1a7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/tw/bkn/cnt/news/20180130/mobile/bkntw-20180130060053988-0130_04011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ba854c5d1232859a377f9a7d43fbc11c4906bb0b","tid":546703,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"三串炸小食賣近50元，台網民:呢種<span style=\"color: red;\">價錢唔</span>會有回頭客，港網民：好抵食"},{"pid":"a9f50f90c54a33b1958d3600a3560c0902207f7e","tid":546703,"uid":123711,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"effafa5135c9070ccf498e79b1acdd7cb5ce4086","tid":546703,"uid":139139,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a9f50f90c54a33b1958d3600a3560c0902207f7e","tid":546703,"uid":123711,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:48:31.000Z","msg":"台灣人太窮"},{"pid":"728667da09b16b4ca199523adb850c82b87fef7d","tid":546703,"uid":21423,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:53:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd8305de43098580ebc2d9f22b3c24d8654a8a10","tid":546703,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"728667da09b16b4ca199523adb850c82b87fef7d","tid":546703,"uid":21423,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:53:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 香港邊有咁貴嘅小食"},{"pid":"f753d9ec7bebee91e17f519eb846780257cb26a7","tid":546703,"uid":12264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T19:36:56.000Z","msg":"叫班台灣仔試下朗豪坊對面間魚蛋檔再出聲"},{"pid":"65427d00577ffe6ebdff2866ff84f21cece7263e","tid":546703,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T21:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm